responseText: NSLOCTEXT("[70199B914E7E03A9706A1499CF20B1FD]", "B33D094745D917FF667FE789BBB3BDA4", "Remind the townspeople and local residents that it\'s past their bedtime. If you run into any of them, just send them home for me. It\'s too risky in this neck of the woods to walk about unfettered.")
